---
// src/components/About.astro
---
<section id="about" class="section-dark py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

    <!-- Label -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-10">
      <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
      <span class="font-body text-amber-500 text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">Our Story</span>
      <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
    </div>

    <!-- Main grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center mb-14">
      <div>
        <span class="gold-line"></span>
        
        <h2 class="section-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white leading-tight mb-8">
          More Than a Lounge.<br />
          <span class="text-amber-400">A Home for Mdantsane.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Founded in 2019, eKoneni Lounge was created with a clear vision: to bring world-class nightlife and premium experiences to Mdantsane. What started as a small lounge quickly grew into a beloved space where people come to celebrate, connect, and feel at home.
        </p>

        <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Today, eKoneni is more than just a venue. We operate a full-service butchery that supplies quality meat for braais and events, host regular amapiano nights with top DJs, and actively give back to the community through feeding schemes, home rebuilding projects, and youth support programmes.
        </p>

        <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Whether you're here to dance until sunrise, enjoy great food and drinks, or simply be in good company — <span class="text-amber-200/80">eKoneni uyakwamkela</span>. You are welcome here.
        </p>

        <!-- Feature pills -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
          <span class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/5 font-body text-amber-300/80 text-xs tracking-wide">Live Amapiano DJs</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/5 font-body text-amber-300/80 text-xs tracking-wide">Premium Cocktails</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/5 font-body text-amber-300/80 text-xs tracking-wide">In-house Butchery</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/5 font-body text-amber-300/80 text-xs tracking-wide">Community Impact</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats row -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-8 border-t border-amber-400/10">
          <div>
            <p class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">6+</p>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1 tracking-wide uppercase">Years Running</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">100s</p>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1 tracking-wide uppercase">Nights Hosted</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">1</p>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1 tracking-wide uppercase">Community. Always.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="about-img rounded-2xl w-full aspect-[4/5] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden relative">
          <img 
            src="/images/lounge/Lounge-image.jpg" 
            alt="eKoneni Lounge interior" 
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-400/8 pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-8 rounded-lg border border-amber-400/5 pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 rounded-xl border-b-2 border-r-2 border-amber-400/25 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-16 h-16 rounded-tl-xl border-t-2 border-l-2 border-amber-400/15 pointer-events-none"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Community teaser strip -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-400/10 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400/5 to-transparent p-8 sm:p-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-6 sm:gap-10">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-amber-400/10 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a4 4 0 00-5-4M9 20H4v-2a4 4 0 015-4m0 0a4 4 0 108 0 4 4 0 01-8 0zM12 12a4 4 0 100-8 4 4 0 000 8z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-white font-bold mb-2">Siyakhathalela — We Care.</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          eKoneni is more than a business. From feeding children in Mdantsane to rebuilding homes for families in need — the owner believes that a thriving community is the foundation of everything. This is what sets eKoneni apart.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="/community" class="flex-shrink-0 btn-outline px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full font-body text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
        See Our Work →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>